7200 REM ENDING
7210 CLS
7212 FOR I=0 TO 11: PUT SPRITE I,(260,200),1: NEXT I
7220 LOCATE 8,7: PRINT "CONGRATULATIONS!"
7230 LOCATE 7,9: PRINT "ALL STAGES CLEARED!"
7240 LOCATE 5,11: PRINT "THANK YOU FOR PLAYING"
7250 LOCATE 9,14: PRINT "MSX SOKOBAN V2"
